{"tid":1490324,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"各位請記住今日氣憤難下、心如刀割嘅感覺","createTime":"2019-08-20T05:24:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T08:44:09.000Z","uid":59693,"like":40,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"07bbba1e3cff0fd489dbe4f0aaf39f9f16644609","tid":1490324,"uid":59693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T05:24:54.000Z","msg":"人始終係會麻木嘅動物<br />\n一旦相近嘅事件出現太多次<br />\n果種由心而發嘅感覺就會愈來愈少，人就會愈來愈麻木，對事件反應就愈少<br />\n<br />\n回顧返由運動開始初期嘅普通警暴<br />\n亂棍毆打市民<br />\n亂射催淚毒氣<br />\n亂射布袋鉛鐵彈，有男教師因此終生失去視力<br />\n有第一個烈士以死相搏，之後二三四五六個<br />\n亂射橡膠子彈<br />\n元朗警黑合作，恐襲地鐵站<br />\n女義士抗爭後 乘Uber 夜歸被強姦<br />\n恐怖份子各區(北角、荃灣)斬人事件，及後無恐怖分子被起訴<br />\n女急救被橡膠射爆單眼<br />\n<br />\n去到今日普通支持者去貼下連儂牆，都比人斬傷<br />\n去到今日又揭發黑警醫院凌虐老人<br />\n<br />\n大家有冇發覺對<span style=\"font-size: large;\">愈遠</span>發生嘅事愈少感受，愈唔強烈？<br />\n<br />\n有幾人人有睇過六位烈士嘅訴求？記得佢地嘅名？由第一個梁烈士開始，之後係咪感覺唔再強烈？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">可悲嘅係，更加多嘅凌虐事件應該係狗屋發生，更多受害者受精神、肉體嘅凌虐後唔敢出黎</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我開呢個目的唔係想去譴責自己及大家<br />\n<br />\n而更係一個提醒，請大家<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">記住運動每一刻令你感到無比痛心、憤怒嘅事，記住果一刻嘅感覺</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔需要被情緒/感覺蒙蔽，但需要佢黎將自己推進，為公義同 無數犧牲咗嘅義士發聲、行動、抗爭以及最後嘅<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">光 復 香 港<br />\n時 代 革 命<br />\n五 大 訴 求<br />\n缺 一 不 可</span></span>"},{"pid":"36c5f26640d79161d4cccdc6ebb3ac398eff44aa","tid":1490324,"uid":59693,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T05:25:27.000Z","msg":"唔好麻木"},{"pid":"1a092882c448b6c2ffc3239d48612a3b542894ee","tid":1490324,"uid":59693,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T05:26:00.000Z","msg":"唔好麻木"},{"pid":"f8cc99c6ca0dccd1a459f921e9ec133057b80d44","tid":1490324,"uid":121255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T05:27:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />keep住每日嘅憤怒"},{"pid":"f53d7018de36d9363a0b49e15cd9208fde6218f9","tid":1490324,"uid":59693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T05:28:07.000Z","msg":"唔好麻木<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aeb9bdc216a6f672257e4be9823af3832d51c80","tid":1490324,"uid":59693,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f8cc99c6ca0dccd1a459f921e9ec133057b80d44","tid":1490324,"uid":121255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T05:27:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />keep住每日嘅憤怒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T05:29:18.000Z","msg":"做最憤怒嘅行動，做最理性嘅決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e3e5c2ecdb323447257670467b80faa385d88b2","tid":1490324,"uid":59693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T05:31:28.000Z","msg":"唔好麻木"},{"pid":"b7e87c334628b255e5d1fc973d637da23236d14f","tid":1490324,"uid":285367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T05:32:42.000Z","msg":"屬於香港既#metoo行動上線啦<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1490165\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1490165</a><br />\n<br />\n起來 不願被欺淩的人們"},{"pid":"d844a17be4430e81c1b52a1bb99204cc42a0bb6c","tid":1490324,"uid":59693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T05:33:26.000Z","msg":"記住呢刻嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"090723c29dc22c15a17fa9f9bca2045298bc571a","tid":1490324,"uid":59693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T05:37:48.000Z","msg":"憤怒與理性可共存<img sr